# Uses calibrated line widths and blot sizing.
# Current saved profile range on this rig is:
# line widths: 0.3 mm to 2.5 mm
# blot sizes: 0.1 mm to 3.5 mm

MOVE 20 20
SETWIDTH 0.75
SETHEADING 0

FORWARD 40 WIDTH 0.6
MOVE 20 32
FORWARD 40
MOVE 20 44
FORWARD 40 WIDTH 0.8

MOVE 80 20
BLOT 0.6
MOVE 80 32
BLOT 0.8
MOVE 80 44
BLOT 1.0

MOVE 120 32
CIRCLE 18